  "timeline": [
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7954",
      "asset": "IMG_7954",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 9.94,
      "note": "The next big space telescope to go up after James Webb is the Nancy Grace Roman"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7956",
      "asset": "IMG_7956",
      "srcIn": 4,
      "srcOut": 10.86,
      "note": "So one of the gizmos that has this thing called a coronagraph, basically it's on"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7958",
      "asset": "IMG_7958",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 11.96,
      "note": "The sci-fi nerd in me likes to think about like, I don't know, a couple hundred"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7959",
      "asset": "IMG_7959",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 14.98,
      "note": "It was a big deal finding any planets at all not too long ago. Now it's, let's f"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7960",
      "asset": "IMG_7960",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 7.74,
      "note": "The Roman Space Telescope is rad as fuck. I'm super excited for it. But what I w"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7961",
      "asset": "IMG_7961",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 22.4,
      "note": "you know Hubble, James Webb, I mean that's a lifetime for some scientists, right"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7962",
      "asset": "IMG_7962",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 12.18,
      "note": "And the Nancy Grace Roman Telescope's no different, but one thing that is differ"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7963",
      "asset": "IMG_7963",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 10.96,
      "note": "the National Reconnaissance Office, and they're basically an agency of the, you"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7969",
      "asset": "IMG_7969",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 17.98,
      "note": "NRO doesn't have these same budget problems. They build a whole mess of them and"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7972",
      "asset": "IMG_7972",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 20.38,
      "note": "Of course, I'm irked because it's like, God, wouldn't it be great if we lived in"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7973",
      "asset": "IMG_7973",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 13.14,
      "note": "But it's just so ironic, like the dichotomy between, you know, these scientists"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7974",
      "asset": "IMG_7974",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 34.34,
      "note": "It's also kind of cool just to think about, maybe cool isn't the right word. So"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7975",
      "asset": "IMG_7975",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 22.1,
      "note": "imagine the capabilities of that telescope. It's like looking down at the ground"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7979",
      "asset": "IMG_7979",
      "srcIn": 0.99,
      "srcOut": 19.96,
      "note": "ironically came with a stipulation. They said you can have this telescope but yo"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7982",
      "asset": "IMG_7982",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 17.48,
      "note": "So look, they're looking for planets orbiting these other stars, other suns. The"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7983",
      "asset": "IMG_7983",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 15.94,
      "note": "What they do is they watch that star for a period of time and they measure the b"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7984",
      "asset": "IMG_7984",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 13.14,
      "note": "by measuring this like dip in brightness and its duration, they can get a sense"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7988",
      "asset": "IMG_7988",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 26.08,
      "note": "But not just that, they can also tell things like what atmosphere is on the plan"
    },
    {
      "id": "c_IMG_7990",
      "asset": "IMG_7990",
      "srcIn": 0,
      "srcOut": 33.9,
      "note": "It's super awesome to think that we have the ability to figure out God knows how"
    }
